#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-np24"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:0.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr "Theravāda Collection on Monastic Law"

#. HTML: </p><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:0.2"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr "Monks’ rules and their analysis"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:0.3"
msgid "Nissaggiyakaṇḍa"
msgstr "The chapter on relinquishment"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:0.4"
msgid "Pattavagga"
msgstr "Monks’ Relinquishment"

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:0.5"
msgid "24. Vassikasāṭikasikkhāpada"
msgstr "24. The training rule on rainy-season robes"

#. HTML: </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc1, pts-cs-bu-np24.1, pts-vp-en2.134, ms1V_2323
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.1"
msgid "Tena samayena buddho bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying at Sāvatthī in the Jeta Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s Monastery."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena bhagavatā bhikkhūnaṃ vassikasāṭikā anuññātā hoti."
msgstr "At that time the Master had allowed the rainy-season robe for the monks."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.3"
msgid "Chabbaggiyā bhikkhū—“bhagavatā vassikasāṭikā anuññātā”ti,"
msgstr "Knowing that this was the case, the monks from the group of six"

#. VAR: paṭikacceva → paṭigacceva (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.4"
msgid "paṭikacceva vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesanti,"
msgstr "went looking for cloth for their rainy-season robes early."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.5"
msgid "paṭikacceva katvā nivāsenti,"
msgstr "And after sewing them early, they wore them."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.6"
msgid "jiṇṇāya vassikasāṭikāya naggā kāyaṃ ovassāpenti."
msgstr "Then, because their rainy-season robes were worn, they bathed naked in the rain."

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.7"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "The monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.8"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized them,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.9"
msgid "“kathañhi nāma chabbaggiyā bhikkhū paṭikacceva vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesissanti, paṭikacceva katvā nivāsessanti, jiṇṇāya vassikasāṭikāya naggā kāyaṃ ovassāpessantī”ti."
msgstr "“How can the monks from the group of six go looking for cloth for their rainy-season robes early, sew them early, and then wear them, and then, because their rainy-season robes are worn, bathe naked in the rain?”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2, ms1V_2324, pts-vp-en2.135
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.10"
msgid "Atha kho te bhikkhū chabbaggiye bhikkhū anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "After criticizing the monks from the group of six in many ways, they told the Master. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.11"
msgid "“saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, paṭikacceva vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesatha?"
msgstr "“Is it true, monks, that you did this?”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.12"
msgid "Paṭikacceva katvā nivāsetha?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.13"
msgid "Jiṇṇāya vassikasāṭikāya naggā kāyaṃ ovassāpethā”ti?"
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.14"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.15"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked them, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.16"
msgid "kathañhi nāma tumhe moghapurisā, paṭikacceva vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesissatha, paṭikacceva katvā nivāsessatha, jiṇṇāya vassikasāṭikāya naggā kāyaṃ ovassāpessatha."
msgstr "Foolish men, how can you go looking for cloth for your rainy-season robes early, sew them early, and then wear them, and then, because your rainy-season robes are worn, bathe naked in the rain?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.17"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisā, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.18"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.18a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc3, pts-vp-pli3.253, ms1V_2325
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.19"
msgid "“‘Māso seso gimhānan’ti bhikkhunā vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesitabbaṃ;"
msgstr "‘When there is a month left of the hot season, a monk may go looking for cloth for his rainy-season robe."

#. VAR: addhamāso → aḍdhamāso (s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.20"
msgid "‘addhamāso seso gimhānan’ti katvā nivāsetabbaṃ."
msgstr "When there is a half-month left, he may sew it and then wear it."

#. VAR: orenaddhamāso → orenaḍdhamāso (s1-3)
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:1.21"
msgid "‘Orena ce māso seso gimhānan’ti vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyeseyya, ‘orenaddhamāso seso gimhānan’ti katvā nivāseyya, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr "If he goes looking for cloth for his rainy-season robe when there is more than a month left of the hot season, or if he sews it and then wears it when there is more than a half-month left, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession.’”"

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. HTML: </h2><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc4, pts-cs-bu-np24.2, ms1V_2326
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.1"
msgid "“Māso seso gimhānan”ti bhikkhunā vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesitabbanti."
msgstr "When there is a month left of the hot season, a monk may go looking for cloth for his rainy-season robe:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.2"
msgid "Ye manussā pubbepi vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ denti te upasaṅkamitvā evamassu vacanīyā—"
msgstr "after approaching those people who previously, too, have given cloth for the rainy-season robes, he should say,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.3"
msgid "“kālo vassikasāṭikāya, samayo vassikasāṭikāya, aññepi manussā vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ dentī”ti."
msgstr "“It’s time for the rainy-season robe/it’s the occasion for the rainy-season robe/other people, too, are giving cloth for the rainy-season robe.”"

#. REF: pts-vp-en2.136
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.4"
msgid "Na vattabbā—"
msgstr "He should not say,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.5"
msgid "“detha me vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ, āharatha me vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ, parivattetha me vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ, cetāpetha me vassikasāṭikacīvaran”ti."
msgstr "“Give me cloth for the rainy-season robe/bring me cloth for the rainy-season robe/buy me cloth for the rainy-season robe/get cloth in exchange for me for the rainy-season robe.”"

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc5, ms1V_2327
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.6"
msgid "“Addhamāso seso gimhānan”ti katvā nivāsetabbanti."
msgstr "When there is a half-month left, he may sew it and then wear it:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.7"
msgid "Addhamāse sese gimhāne katvā nivāsetabbaṃ."
msgstr "after sewing it during the last half-month of the hot season, he may wear it."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc6, ms1V_2328
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.8"
msgid "“Orena ce māso seso gimhānan”ti"
msgstr "When there is more than a month left of the hot season:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.9"
msgid "atirekamāse sese gimhāne vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesati, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "if he goes looking for cloth for the rainy-season robe when there is more than a month left of the hot season, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

#. HTML: </span></p><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc7, ms1V_2329
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.10"
msgid "“Orenaddhamāso seso gimhānan”ti"
msgstr "When there is more than a half-month left of the hot season:"

#. HTML: </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.11"
msgid "atirekaddhamāse sese gimhāne katvā nivāseti, nissaggiyaṃ hoti."
msgstr "if he wears it after sewing it when there is more than a half-month left of the hot season, it becomes subject to relinquishment."

#. HTML: </span></p><hr><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.12"
msgid "Nissajjitabbaṃ saṃghassa vā gaṇassa vā puggalassa vā."
msgstr "The rainy-season robe should be relinquished to an Order, a group, or an individual."

#. HTML: <span class="kamma"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.13"
msgid "Evañca pana, bhikkhave, nissajjitabbaṃ …"
msgstr "“And, monks, it should be relinquished in this way. …"

#. HTML: <span class="pe"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.14"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr "To be expanded as in [Relinquishment 1, paragraphs 13–17](pli-tv-bu-vb-np1#13), with appropriate substitutions. "

#. HTML: </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.15"
msgid "“idaṃ me, bhante, vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ atirekamāse sese gimhāne pariyiṭṭhaṃ atirekaddhamāse sese gimhāne katvā paridahitaṃ nissaggiyaṃ."
msgstr "‘Venerables, this cloth for the rainy-season robe which I went looking for when there was more than a month left of the hot season and/or which I wore after sewing it when there was more than a half-month left of the hot season is to be relinquished."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.16"
msgid "Imāhaṃ saṃghassa nissajjāmī”ti … pe …"
msgstr "I relinquish it to the Order.’ …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.17"
msgid "dadeyyāti … pe …"
msgstr "the Order should give …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.18"
msgid "dadeyyunti … pe …"
msgstr "you should give …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.19"
msgid "āyasmato dammīti."
msgstr "‘I give this cloth for the rainy-season robe back to you.’”"

#. HTML: </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.19a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc8, ms1V_2330
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.20"
msgid "Atirekamāse sese gimhāne atirekasaññī vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesati, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If there is more than a month left of the hot season, and he perceives it as more, and he goes looking for cloth for a rainy-season robe, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.21"
msgid "Atirekamāse sese gimhāne vematiko vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesati, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If there is more than a month left of the hot season, but he is unsure if there is, and he goes looking for cloth for a rainy-season robe, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.22"
msgid "Atirekamāse sese gimhāne ūnakasaññī vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesati, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If there is more than a month left of the hot season, but he perceives it as less, and he goes looking for cloth for a rainy-season robe, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9, ms1V_2331, pts-vp-en2.137
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.23"
msgid "Atirekaddhamāse sese gimhāne atirekasaññī katvā nivāseti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If there is more than a half-month left of the hot season, and he perceives it as more, and he wears the rainy-season robe after sewing it, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.24"
msgid "Atirekaddhamāse sese gimhāne vematiko katvā nivāseti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If there is more than a half-month left of the hot season, but he is unsure if there is, and he wears the rainy-season robe after sewing it, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.25"
msgid "Atirekaddhamāse sese gimhāne ūnakasaññī katvā nivāseti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr "If there is more than a half-month left of the hot season, but he perceives it as less, and he wears the rainy-season robe after sewing it, he commits an offense entailing relinquishment and confession."

#. HTML: </p><p><span class="rule"> 
#. REF: sc10, ms1V_2332
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.26"
msgid "Satiyā vassikasāṭikāya naggo kāyaṃ ovassāpeti, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If he has a rainy-season robe, but he bathes naked in the rain, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. HTML: </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.27"
msgid "Ūnakamāse sese gimhāne atirekasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If there is less than a month left of the hot season, but he perceives it as more, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.28"
msgid "Ūnakamāse sese gimhāne vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If there is less than a month left of the hot season, but he is unsure if there is, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.29"
msgid "Ūnakamāse sese gimhāne ūnakasaññī, anāpatti."
msgstr "If there is less than a month left of the hot season, and he perceives it as less, there is no offense."

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11, pts-vp-pli3.254, ms1V_2333
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.30"
msgid "Ūnakaddhamāse sese gimhāne atirekasaññī, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If there is less than a half-month left of the hot season, but he perceives it as more, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.31"
msgid "Ūnakaddhamāse sese gimhāne vematiko, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "If there is less than a half-month left of the hot season, but he is unsure if there is, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.32"
msgid "Ūnakaddhamāse sese gimhāne ūnakasaññī, anāpatti."
msgstr "If there is less than a half-month left of the hot season, and he perceives it as less, there is no offense."

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.32a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: sc12, ms1V_2334
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.33"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.34"
msgid "“māso seso gimhānan”ti vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesati,"
msgstr "if he goes looking for cloth for the rainy-season robe when there is a month left of the hot season;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.35"
msgid "“addhamāso seso gimhānan”ti katvā nivāseti,"
msgstr "if he wears the rainy-season robe after sewing it when there is a half-month left of the hot season;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.36"
msgid "“ūnakamāso seso gimhānan”ti vassikasāṭikacīvaraṃ pariyesati,"
msgstr "if he goes looking for cloth for the rainy-season robe when there is less than a month left of the hot season;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.37"
msgid "“ūnakaddhamāso seso gimhānan”ti katvā nivāseti,"
msgstr "if he wears the rainy-season robe after sewing it when there is less than a half-month left of the hot season;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.38"
msgid "pariyiṭṭhāya vassikasāṭikāya vassaṃ ukkaḍḍhiyyati,"
msgstr "if, after looking for a rainy-season robe, he postpones the rains residence;"

#. REF: pts-vp-en2.138
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.39"
msgid "nivatthāya vassikasāṭikāya vassaṃ ukkaḍḍhiyyati, dhovitvā nikkhipitabbaṃ;"
msgstr "if, after wearing a rainy-season robe, he postpones the rains residence (in which case he should wash it and store it and then use it at the right time);"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.40"
msgid "samaye nivāsetabbaṃ, acchinnacīvarassa,"
msgstr "if his robe has been stolen;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.41"
msgid "naṭṭhacīvarassa,"
msgstr "if his robe has been lost;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.42"
msgid "āpadāsu,"
msgstr "if there are dangers;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.43"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.44"
msgid "ādikammikassāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. HTML: </p><hr><p class="endsutta">
#. REF: sc13, ms1V_2335
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np24:2.45"
msgid "Vassikasāṭikasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ catutthaṃ."
msgstr "The fourth rule, the training rule on rainy-season robes, is finished."
